<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٩٥١ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2594">‌أَبُو دَاوُدَ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1620">‌حَمَّادٌ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5183">‌قَتَادَةَ </a>، عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1389">‌الْحَسَنِ </a>، <a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٢٢٧⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2651">‌سَمُرَةَ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> قَالَ النَّبِيُّ صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ: <span class="c2">«كُلُّ غُلَامٍ مُرْتَهَنٌ بِعَقِيقَتِهِ»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>